_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136370/extras/84f1ebb3583318665fd7d06aa4f372e5.poster.avif?t=1724396440\" width=620 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136370/extras/84f1ebb3583318665fd7d06aa4f372e5.webm?t=1724396440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136370/extras/84f1ebb3583318665fd7d06aa4f372e5.mp4?t=1724396440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Battle your way through diverse stages as you protect every part of the hand-drawn, pixel art landscapes of New Port City.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136370/extras/404c26f4dc17edf724a782ce5a8664b7.avif?t=1724396440\" width=601 height=76 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136370/extras/0bf6736ceb1039fcd8bdec65afe3c56f.poster.avif?t=1724396440\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136370/extras/0bf6736ceb1039fcd8bdec65afe3c56f.webm?t=1724396440\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136370/extras/0bf6736ceb1039fcd8bdec65afe3c56f.mp4?t=1724396440\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fuel your fight with the bespoke metal soundtrack. Thrashing guitars and pulsing drums propel you forward through enemy forces. This is the genre as it was always meant to be heard.",
